<div class="app-card-container">
  <div class="card" style="width: 65rem;">
    <h1>About Me</h1>
    <hr/>

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-4">
        <%= image_tag "me.jpg", width: 300, alt: "profile image", class: "profile-img" %>
        <div class="skills">
          <% @skills.each do |skill| %>
            <div class="skill">

              <h4>
                <%= skill.title %></h4>
              <div class="progress">
                <div class="progress-bar progress-bar-striped bg-warning" role="progressbar" aria-valuenow="<%= skill.percent_used %>" aria-valuemax="100" style="width: <%= skill.percent_used %>%"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          <% end %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="col-md-8">
        <p>I'm a web developer with experience working with Rails, Go, Javascipt, and React. My academic backgroud is in Computational Mathematics.</p>

        <p>I'm a huge nerd for programming languages and digging into the details of how they work. I love spending some spare time working on interpreters and compilers so that languages seem less like black magic. </p>

        <p>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#jobHistory" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="jobHistory">

            Job History
          </button>

          <button class="btn btn-primary" type="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#edHistory" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="edHistory">

            Education
          </button>
        </p>


        <p>

          <div class="collapse" id="jobHistory">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Sphere 2016-2017 Backend Developer
            </div>

          </div>
          <div class="collapse" id="edHistory">
            <div class="card card-body">
              Brooklyn College 2014 Computational Mathematics
            </div>

          </div>
        </p>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
